{"tid":1725223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警柴灣跌子彈　消息：休班警柴灣被圍毆　舉槍示警跌下","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:13:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9e22969c0ca7920c2509ba3aaf7e694ed57ad0","tid":1725223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"反修例風波升溫，多區示威衝突持續。根據網上所傳，周五晚（15日）有人於柴灣拾到子彈，並傳有警察發射實彈真槍。不過消息透露，一名休班警員周五晚約9時半，經過柴灣街市期間遭一批示威者圍毆，該警員以警棍保護自己不果後舉槍示警，期間跌出一粒子彈，其後由衝鋒隊拾回。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上傳言，今晚（15日）有人於柴灣拾到子彈，並傳有警察發射真槍；而流傳的圖片顯示有人以紙巾手持一粒懷疑子彈。據消息稱，有一名休班警員於晚上9時44分在經過柴灣街市期間，遭一群示威者攻擊，他用警棍保護自己不果後舉槍；期間，跌出一粒子彈；該子彈後已經被衝鋒隊發現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/398920/%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%B7%8C%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E8%88%89%E6%A7%8D%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E8%B7%8C%E4%B8%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F398920%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%259C%258D%25E6%25AF%2586-%25E8%2588%2589%25E6%25A7%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25B7%258C%25E4%25B8%258B&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=ec58df33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/398920/%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%B7%8C%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%B4%E7%81%A3%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86-%E8%88%89%E6%A7%8D%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E8%B7%8C%E4%B8%8B</a>"},{"pid":"13bd82e827d6eabf90ea6b45ae96a926fd0f5c90","tid":1725223,"uid":153778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"休班都有炮？便衣呀"},{"pid":"833bf7390602fe60